title: Add missing cli args to usage

body:
As the title says. Feel free to correct the descriptions if I misunderstood their usage.

Fixes #360
Worth making sure that these are also mirrored in the usage section of README.md

issue.title: Help message missing newly introduced arguments to run flux models
issue.body:
The following arguments are not listed when running `./sd -h`
```
--diffusion-model
--clip_l
--t5xxl
--vae-on-cpu
--clip-on-cpu
```
I might be missing some.
